Slut
__NOTOC__


A '''Slut''' is a girl or [[woman]] who spends [[moar]] time [[fucking]] than making [[sammich|sammiches]]. While [[Whores]] demand [[Scissoring|payment for their services]], usually [[money]], [[skank|drugs]], [[camwhore|items from their wish lists]], or [[Attention whore|attention]], sluts love the [[cock]] for itself.


==The Nature of the Beast==
[[Image:Inpublik.jpg|thumb|right|150px|Slut in the wild. CROIKY!]]
[[Image:Touellette on 4chan biggest slut ever.png|thumb|right|150px|Perfect example of a Canadian slut on 4chan!.]]

Sluts are prone to many of the same difficulties as whores, namely [[STD]]s and threats of [[pwnage]] from angry cheated-on girlfriends. In addition, while whores have a steady income stream, sluts are usually broke.

Many sluts are [[16 year old girls]] who pretend to be 20. Because their fathers never molested them, they are lonely and need the [[cock]] inside of them to make them feel better about their future careers as prostitutes and members of [[government]] [[Satire|(which is about the same as being a prostitute)]]. 

Other sluts are usually [[emo]] and want some attention because their boyfriend left them for [[morrissey|a girl with a greater collection of scars from  "attempts"]].

The unifying characteristic of sluts is this: they will not sleep with you (Is she a virgin? Has she been faithful to the same man for twenty years? Does she give blow jobs for a nickel apiece behind the bowling alley? Doesn't matter) or, ironically, they will sleep with you too readily.  

Either way, she is a slut until she sleeps with you. A "slut" who does sleep with you is no longer a slut, but a "cool chick" who knows how to have a good time. Then, when you get tired of her vagina and it's time to move on, she goes back to being a slut again.

A girl can also qualify for sluthood by sleeping with your skank-ass boyfriend, because she totally should've known he was lying when he said you didn't exist after having seen you with him for months.

